question: icu 첫 24시간 lactate 평균 vs 사망 여부 알려줘
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN A.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status, AVG(C.VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate
FROM ADMISSIONS A
JOIN CHARTEVENTS C ON A.HADM_ID = C.HADM_ID
JOIN D_ITEMS D ON C.ITEMID = D.ITEMID
WHERE C.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND D.LABEL = 'Lactate' AND C.CHARTTIME <= A.ADMITTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
GROUP BY CASE WHEN A.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END

question: icu 첫 24시간 lactate 평균 vs 사망 여부 알려줘
sql:
WITH ICU_ADMISSIONS AS ( 
    SELECT A.HADM_ID, A.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG, MIN(I.INTIME) AS ICU_INTIME 
    FROM ADMISSIONS A 
    JOIN ICUSTAYS I ON A.SUBJECT_ID = I.SUBJECT_ID AND A.HADM_ID = I.HADM_ID 
    GROUP BY A.HADM_ID, A.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG 
), LACTATE_MEASUREMENTS AS ( 
    SELECT C.HADM_ID, C.CHARTTIME, C.VALUENUM 
    FROM CHARTEVENTS C 
    JOIN D_ITEMS D ON C.ITEMID = D.ITEMID 
    WHERE ROWNUM <= 5000 AND F.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND D.LABEL = 'Lactate' AND C.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL 
), FIRST_24HR_LACTATE AS ( 
    SELECT L.HADM_ID, L.VALUENUM 
    FROM LACTATE_MEASUREMENTS L 
    JOIN ICU_ADMISSIONS IA ON L.HADM_ID = IA.HADM_ID 
    WHERE L.CHARTTIME <= IA.ICU_INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR 
) 
SELECT CASE WHEN IA.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status, 
       AVG(F.VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate 
FROM FIRST_24HR_LACTATE F 
JOIN ICU_ADMISSIONS IA ON F.HADM_ID = IA.HADM_ID 
GROUP BY CASE WHEN IA.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END

question: icu 첫 24시간 lactate 평균 vs 사망 여부 알려줘
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status, AVG(c.VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate
FROM CHARTEVENTS c
JOIN D_ITEMS d ON c.ITEMID = d.ITEMID
JOIN ICUSTAYS i ON c.STAY_ID = i.STAY_ID
JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON i.HADM_ID = a.HADM_ID
WHERE c.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND d.LABEL = 'Lactate' AND c.CHARTTIME BETWEEN i.INTIME AND i.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
GROUP BY CASE WHEN a.HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END

question: icu 첫 24시간 lactate 평균 vs 사망 여부 알려줘
sql:
WITH lactate_events AS (
    SELECT c.HADM_ID, c.VALUENUM
    FROM CHARTEVENTS c
    JOIN D_ITEMS d ON c.ITEMID = d.ITEMID
    JOIN ICUSTAYS i ON c.STAY_ID = i.STAY_ID
    WHERE VALUENUM IS NOT NULL AND c.VALUENUM IS NOT NULL 
      AND d.LABEL = 'Lactate' 
      AND c.CHARTTIME BETWEEN i.INTIME AND i.INTIME + INTERVAL '24' HOUR
),
patient_mortality AS (
    SELECT HADM_ID, CASE WHEN HOSPITAL_EXPIRE_FLAG = 1 THEN 'Deceased' ELSE 'Survived' END AS mortality_status
    FROM ADMISSIONS
)
SELECT pm.mortality_status, AVG(VALUENUM) AS avg_lactate
FROM lactate_events le
JOIN patient_mortality pm ON le.HADM_ID = pm.HADM_ID
GROUP BY pm.mortality_status
